Cloud Deployment Models

# Public Cloud

- Most common deployment
- AWS, Microsoft Azure, IBM Bluemix, SalesForce etc

# Private Cloud

- Exclusive use by a single organisation comprising multiple customers, like business units
- Workds the same way as Public Cloud, but the services are provided to internal customers

# Community Cloud

- Provisioned for exclusive use by a specific community of consumers from organisations that have shared concerns
- Least common, sometimes used in government environments

# Hybrid Cloud

- Consusts or two or more distinct cloud infrastructures
